    "body": "I fixed it by just writing it in Rust and compiling it to an exe then doing so:\n\n```toml\ncommand = 'C:\\Users\\Hp\\.config\\get-time.exe'\nshell = \"cmd\" # Using pwsh/powershell is still awfully slower.\n```\n\nAlthough that works, I still think looking into why powershell is so slow is needed, so I'll leave the issue opened.\n\nEdit: Missing a ``` ` ```",
